text: Sohail Sultan (), is a Pakistani politician who is a member of the National Assembly of Pakistan. ==Political career== Sultan won the 2024 Pakistani general election from NA-4 Swat-III as an Independent candidate. He received 88,009 votes while runners up Muhammad Saleem Khan of Awami National Party received 20,890 votes. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Pakistani MNAs Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
